{"tid":1497381,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一邊同台灣講一國兩制係謊言，一邊強調我哋唔係搞獨立尊重一國兩制","createTime":"2019-08-23T02:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T03:31:38.000Z","uid":25643,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0925798d2072b3f89988af4c05cd003bbbe5df51","tid":1497381,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:49:59.000Z","msg":"其實大家有無懷疑自己精神分裂？<br />\n明知一國兩制下只會繼續沉淪<br />\n<br />\n因為驚畀大陸口實？<br />\n就算你點講我唔係搞獨立尊重一個中國一國兩制<br />\n都會俾大陸打成港獨分子攪顏色革命<br />\n<br />\n因為爭取大陸人支持？<br />\n大陸消息都被禁制，絕大部分人都係睇偏頗嘅事實<br />\n就算少數同情嘅人都被迅速滅聲<br />\n<br />\n認清事實，爭取民主同攪獨立係冇分別，除非你接受人大831式民主<br />\n因為共產黨只在乎權力，貪婪咁不斷攫取控制他人嘅權力，亦唔願意放棄權力<br />\n全面普選同獨立對佢嚟講都係失去控制香港嘅權力<br />\n<br />\n點解要自制白色恐怖，放棄向世人高呼獨立自主嘅渴望？<br />\n拒絕沉淪，唯有獨立"},{"pid":"26f868c3591cf1832d80aa151fb71958b14a38d2","tid":1497381,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:52:43.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU！而家搭車犯法呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9EGvnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9EGvnL.jpg&h=9da42bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKSEg2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKSEg2M.jpg&h=20a2e6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/now5W2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnow5W2M.jpg&h=db034c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC19Ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr